    "description": "《Path of Yuusha》为一款以勇者养成学校「Yuusha academy 勇者学园」作为舞台的模拟策略游戏。玩家除了可以体验上课、工作等繁忙的学生生活外，还可以使用各种道具来自由装饰自己的房间，订定每周的时程表，例如安排时间在学校学习各种咒文魔法、在魔女小屋学习链金术、或是在餐厅打工赚钱等等，依照玩家自己的喜好与需求，透过每周各式各样的活动时间安排，将自己的角色培育成能够独当一面的勇者。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234950/extras/55718b9830932ee6e1d5018b13dc9215.poster.avif?t=1672910599\" width=600 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234950/extras/55718b9830932ee6e1d5018b13dc9215.webm?t=1672910599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234950/extras/55718b9830932ee6e1d5018b13dc9215.mp4?t=1672910599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >管理每周的行程</h2>你需要依照角色的需求安排你每周的行程，除了安排课程培育角色或打工赚钱外，也需要安排适当的自由与休息时间来降低角色压力，才能让玩家的勇者养成更加事半功倍。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234950/extras/1947d80dbe7766e4e298e78e6301f624.poster.avif?t=1672910599\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234950/extras/1947d80dbe7766e4e298e78e6301f624.webm?t=1672910599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234950/extras/1947d80dbe7766e4e298e78e6301f624.mp4?t=1672910599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自由的装饰自己的房间</h2>玩家可以使用在地城中获得各种道具来自由的装饰自己的房间，家具还能提供额外的能力加成。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234950/extras/ae07d60cbda9dd2fd9d25c9c1ad0dd2f.poster.avif?t=1672910599\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234950/extras/ae07d60cbda9dd2fd9d25c9c1ad0dd2f.webm?t=1672910599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234950/extras/ae07d60cbda9dd2fd9d25c9c1ad0dd2f.mp4?t=1672910599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >饲养宠物</h2>你可以捕捉及饲养各式各样的宠物，不同宠物会有各自的专精能力，有些能和你一同战斗，有些能够帮助你种植草药等等。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234950/extras/3e7187ce286e02b5d18bc60b30778e2c.poster.avif?t=1672910599\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234950/extras/3e7187ce286e02b5d18bc60b30778e2c.webm?t=1672910599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234950/extras/3e7187ce286e02b5d18bc60b30778e2c.mp4?t=1672910599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与其他冒险一同探险</h2>前往冒险者公会与其他冒险者交谈与组队，一同前往地城中探险，击败地城中的敌人以获得宝箱提升角色的能力值。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234950/extras/966c8c6897680d23b543806fb817a80b.poster.avif?t=1672910599\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234950/extras/966c8c6897680d23b543806fb817a80b.webm?t=1672910599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234950/extras/966c8c6897680d23b543806fb817a80b.mp4?t=1672910599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
